Sven,

The thermal diffusion coefficient is neglected (set to zero) for the
mixture-averaged transport.

In any case, you do not need that to get the lewis number.  You only need
the species mass diffusion coefficient and the thermal diffusion coefficient
(thermal conductivity / density / heat capacity).

James



